00:20:52,469 --> 00:20:54,769
Itu bukan urusanku.

269
00:20:56,409 --> 00:20:58,280
Kenapa kamu ingin menemuiku?

270
00:21:00,209 --> 00:21:02,419
Aku ingin menemui Pak Koo Gi Baek.

271
00:21:03,650 --> 00:21:05,219
Kenapa?

272
00:21:05,719 --> 00:21:07,550
Karena aku mencemaskan Jung Hee.

273
