275
00:21:30,310 --> 00:21:31,780
Ya, kurasa begitu.

276
00:21:31,979 --> 00:21:33,409
Katakanlah.

277
00:21:36,150 --> 00:21:38,590
Menurutmu Jung Hee benar-benar melihat

278
00:21:41,719 --> 00:21:46,030
