279
00:21:47,390 --> 00:21:49,100
Bagaimana menurutmu?

280
00:21:49,259 --> 00:21:50,659
Kurasa dia melihatnya.

281
00:21:50,900 --> 00:21:53,100
Mungkin Gi Baek juga tahu.

282
00:21:53,469 --> 00:21:56,499
