Dia...

288
00:22:12,489 --> 00:22:13,550
Racun?

289
00:22:13,850 --> 00:22:16,120
Apa maksudnya?

290
00:22:21,929 --> 00:22:24,100
Aku meminta para staf bersiap.

291
00:22:24,800 --> 00:22:27,229
Kubilang kamu bisa syuting film

292
